trans-unit.source: Animates the value of a property that takes a <xref href="System.Windows.Rect"></xref> along a set of key frames.
trans-unit.target: Animerer verdien i en egenskap som tar en <xref href="System.Windows.Rect"> </xref> langs et sett med nøkkelen for forhandleren.

trans-unit.source: A key frame animation's target values are defined by its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A> property, which contains a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame> objects.
trans-unit.target: En nøkkel for animasjonen målverdier er definert av den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A>egenskap, som inneholder en samling av <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame> defines a segment of the animation with its own target <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame.Value%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame>definerer segmentet animasjonen med egne mål <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame.Value%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame>

trans-unit.source: When the animation runs, it progresses from one key value to the next at the specified key times.
trans-unit.target: Når animasjonen kjører, den går videre fra én nøkkelverdien til neste på den angitte nøkkelkolonner ganger.

trans-unit.source: There are three types of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame> classes, one for each supported interpolation method: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearRectKeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteRectKeyFrame>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineRectKeyFrame>.
trans-unit.target: Det finnes tre typer <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame>klasser, én for hver støttede interpoleringsmetode: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearRectKeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteRectKeyFrame>, og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineRectKeyFrame>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineRectKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteRectKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearRectKeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame>

trans-unit.source: Unlike a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimation>, a RectAnimationUsingKeyFrames can have more than two target values.
trans-unit.target: I motsetning til en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimation>, en RectAnimationUsingKeyFrames kan ha flere enn to målverdier.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimation>

trans-unit.source: You can also control the interpolation method of individual <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame> segments.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også kontrollere interpoleringsmetode over enkelte <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame>segmenter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectKeyFrame>

trans-unit.source: Calculates a value that represents the current value of the property being animated, as determined by this instance of <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimationUsingKeyFrames"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Beregner en verdi som representerer gjeldende verdi for egenskapen blir animerte, i henhold til denne forekomsten av <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.RectAnimationUsingKeyFrames"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If `defaultOriginValue` is the first in the composition chain, this value will be the snapshot value (if one is available) or the base property value; otherwise this value will be the value returned by the previous animation in the chain with an <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.AnimationClock> that is not stopped.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `defaultOriginValue` er først i sammensetningen-kjede denne verdien være statisk utvalg-verdi (Hvis det finnes) eller base egenskapsverdien; Hvis denne verdien blir verdien som returneres av forrige animasjon i kjeden med en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.AnimationClock>som ikke er stoppet.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.AnimationClock>

trans-unit.source: The `defaultDestinationValue` is the base value if the animation is in the first composition layer of animations on a property; otherwise, the value is the output value from the previous composition layer of animations for the property.
trans-unit.target: Den `defaultDestinationValue` er grunnleggende verdi Hvis animasjonen er det første sammensetning laget for animasjoner på en egenskap, ellers verdien er output-verdi fra den forrige sammensetningen lag med animasjoner for egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The suggested origin value, used if the animation does not have its own explicitly set start value.
trans-unit.target: Anbefalte origo-verdien brukes hvis animasjonen ikke har et eget eksplisitt angitt startverdi.

trans-unit.source: The suggested destination value, used if the animation does not have its own explicitly set end value.
trans-unit.target: Anbefalte mål-verdien brukes hvis animasjonen ikke har et eget eksplisitt angitt slutte verdi.

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.AnimationClock"> </xref> som genererer den <> </> *> eller <> </> *> brukes av verten animasjonen.

trans-unit.source: If the last key frame of this animation is a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeyTime"></xref>, then this value is used as the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Clock.NaturalDuration*>; otherwise it will be one second.
